item.title: Is the Husker Football Team Cursed?
item.description: Husker Football has suffered greatly over the past few years. The number of fans wanting Frost to be fired has grown, but so has the number of fans supporting Frost and the team’s comeback story. So, what’s the deal? Is Nebraska unlucky, or do they actually just suck? To even begin figuring out that answer, I need to download all of my libraries that I will need to create these charts.
